description.fr: {Weapon:57} et {Summoning:958} doivent survivre 5 tours. \--- SCORE\_: Dégâts infligés aux personnages et {%KEYWORD.OBJECTMECHANISM.NAME, plural:other} adverses. \--- DÉFAITE\_: Vous perdez la moitié de vos points.
description.en: {Weapon:57} and {Summoning:958} must survive 5 turns. \--- SCORE: Damage done to opposing characters and {%KEYWORD.OBJECTMECHANISM.NAME, plural:other}. \--- DEFEAT: You lose half your points.
description.es: {Weapon:57} y {Summoning:958} deben sobrevivir 5 turnos. \--- PUNTUACIÓN: Daños infligidos a los personajes y {%KEYWORD.OBJECTMECHANISM.NAME, plural:other} enemigos. \--- DERROTA: Pierdes la mitad de tus puntos.
description.de: {Weapon:57} und {Summoning:958} müssen 5\_Runden überleben. \--- PUNKTE: Bei gegnerischen Charakteren und {%KEYWORD.OBJECTMECHANISM.NAME, plural:other} verursachter Schaden. \--- NIEDERLAGE: Du verlierst die Hälfte deiner Punkte.
description.pt: {Weapon:57} e {Summoning:958} devem sobreviver 5 turnos. \--- PONTUAÇÃO: Danos infligidos aos personagens e {%KEYWORD.OBJECTMECHANISM.NAME, plural:other} adversários. \--- DERROTA: Você perde a metade dos seus pontos.
